WEBVTT

10:36.880 --> 10:39.000 line:80%
They made my grandson like this,

10:39.000 --> 10:41.550 line:80%
and... and she's acting
as if she's completely in the right!

10:41.550 --> 10:42.350 line:80%
Stop shouting!

10:42.350 --> 10:43.040 line:80%
Alright.

10:43.640 --> 10:44.670 line:80%
